Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie有股強烈的正義感\N{\fs38}Annie has a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只強烈希望能與鄰居融洽相處\N{\fs38}I have a strong sense of wanting to get along with my neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在這種場合 我能說Annie什么嗎\N{\fs38}But can I say something to Annie in these situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不能  - 聽著 我不知道你\N{\fs38}- No, I cannot. - Listen, I don't know what cave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前活在哪個原始山洞里的...\N{\fs38}you dragged your knuckles out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 親愛的 我們的預約  - 但在這幢樓里\N{\fs38}- Honey, our reservation... - ...but in this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都要有禮貌 聽懂沒\N{\fs38}we believe in manners, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯你是初來到文明社會\N{\fs38}You're apparently new to manners and society...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 有興趣一起出去吃晚飯嗎  - 呃\N{\fs38}- Do you wanna go out to dinner? - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛見到上次在電梯遇到的人 超冷淡\N{\fs38}Just saw the elevator guy... total cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問他到幾樓 他自己按了樓層\N{\fs38}I asked him what floor. He pushed his own button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 親愛的 我知道你多\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, sweetie, I know how you like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡按電梯按扭\N{\fs38}to push those buttons yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我夠得著\N{\fs38}Well, the ones I can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 Harris發來的 說有個卡拉OK派對\N{\fs38}Crap. It's Harris. It's about the karaoke party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然很懷念退休的日子\N{\fs38}Suddenly I miss being retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年 Mike的老板就喜歡\N{\fs38}Every year, Mike's boss bundles
