Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是為了滿足\N{\fs38}But it's really just his
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己打扮和在人們面前唱歌的私欲\N{\fs38}excuse to get up and sing in front of a crowd.
