Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們總是搬出各種缺席的借口\N{\fs38}And we've been known to come up with excuses for why we can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 就說我大姨媽去世了\N{\fs38}I know. I'll say my great aunt died.
