Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 就說我發燒了  - 這個不錯\N{\fs38}- I could come down with a fever. - That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么一來 我還不用回答其他附帶問題\N{\fs38}That way, I don't have to answer any follow-up questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如"你大姨媽叫什么"\N{\fs38}like "What was your aunt's name?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于看演唱會的事 你們太不講理了\N{\fs38}You guys are being totally unreasonable about the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Amy的家人還說會載她去呢  - 哪個家人\N{\fs38}- Amy's family offered to drive. - Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那個22歲胡子都長到脖子上的哥哥嗎\N{\fs38}Try her 22-year-old brother with a full neck-beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 猜猜我干了什么  - 你買了條狗啊\N{\fs38}- Look what I just got. - You got a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在說我新弄的頭發 不過的確 我買了條狗\N{\fs38}Oh, I was referring to my blowout, but, yes, I did get a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小東西可以幫我增加點男人緣哦\N{\fs38}This little guy is gonna help me meet guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那你可以叫它破冰者  - 這個好\N{\fs38}- You should name him Icebreaker. - Genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給小孩取名不太是你的強項\N{\fs38}Naming children really isn't really your thing,
