Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得小時候你帶回家的Banjo嗎\N{\fs38}Remember you brought home Banjo when we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果是誰在照顧Banjo呢 是我\N{\fs38}Who ended up taking care of Banjo? I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么有預感事件會重演呢\N{\fs38}Why do I have a feeling that's gonna happen again this time?
