Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全有能力照顧一只寵物\N{\fs38}She's perfectly capable of owning a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得她對這狗就三分鐘熱度嗎\N{\fs38}You don't think she's gonna flake on this dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了這么久我有多不靠譜 還是沒說說我的發型\N{\fs38}A lot of talk about how I'm a flake, not a word about my blowout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是覺得 我知道\N{\fs38}I don't think it. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不 我們賭一次\N{\fs38}In fact, I'm willing to bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了 我可以去看演唱會\N{\fs38}What do you say... if I win, I get to go to the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我喜歡這種穩贏的賭局  - 等著瞧\N{\fs38}- I love a bet I can't lose. - You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像跟小朋友打賭一樣沒挑戰\N{\fs38}This is going to be like going to a concert from a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 該死 你怎么在這里\N{\fs38}Oh, come on! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得去啊 Mike 我是說\N{\fs38}You got to be there, Mike. I mean, it's not just
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不僅僅是個省錢的群體生日會 \N{\fs38}a money-saving mass birthday party. It's a celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個古日本卡拉OK的文化盛宴\N{\fs38}of the ancient Japanese art of kara-o-kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 絕不容錯過哦  - 聽起來不錯哦\N{\fs38}- You can't miss that. - Well, as awesome as that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 Annie可能把感冒傳染給我了\N{\fs38}uh, I-I-I... the thing is I think Annie's gotten me sick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 Mike 我們還喝了同一杯奶昔\N{\fs38}Oh, damn it, Mike. We split a milkshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在害我啊 我明天還要演唱呢\N{\fs38}Man, what are you doing to me? I got to sing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你用另一根吸管嘛\N{\fs38}I told you to get an extra straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harris 聽著 我得走了\N{\fs38}Harris, listen, I got to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體允許的話 我會盡量去的 \N{\fs38}We'll be there... health permitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天氣可真夠受的是吧\N{\fs38}This is some weather we're having, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這么說\N{\fs38}When I say that, I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是隨便閑聊而已 我是做新聞的\N{\fs38}just making small talk. I work in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有氣象臺的內部消息\N{\fs38}I've got access to a Doppler 9000, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}Doppler 9000 氣象雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于昨晚 我的妻子Annie 她有點\N{\fs38}Uh, about last night, my wife, Annie, she got a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 暴躁  - 有點\N{\fs38}- snippy. - A little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她教訓了我一整路啊\N{\fs38}She lectured me the entire elevator ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還跟到我家門口\N{\fs38}followed me to my door...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我鄰居家門\N{\fs38}Well, my neighbor's door, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我才不想讓她知道我住哪  - 明智\N{\fs38}- I didn't want her to know where I live. - That's good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是這樣的 Annie最近不太好\N{\fs38}The thing is, Annie's going through a rough patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么意思  - 就是 她有點...你懂的\N{\fs38}- What do you mean? - Well, she's a little... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不懂  - 她最近停藥了\N{\fs38}- No, I don't. - She's a little bit... off her meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒想到 她還好吧\N{\fs38}Oh. I had no idea. Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她實際上 不太好 不好\N{\fs38}Well, she's... not really, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒非常不穩定\N{\fs38}No, it's terrible mood swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天好 一天壞的\N{\fs38}One day, yay! Another day, boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉 她是躁郁癥嗎  - 對 就是這個\N{\fs38}- If I may ask, is she bipolar? - Yes. Perfect. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是典型的躁郁癥 就是這個\N{\fs38}She's... she's classic bipolar. It's a whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我是精神科醫生 天天和這種病打交道\N{\fs38}I'm so sorry. I'm a psychiatrist. I deal with that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就不用多說了\N{\fs38}Oh, so we don't have to talk about this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問一問她在接受什么藥物治療嗎\N{\fs38}If I may ask, um... what kind of medication is she on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些圓圓小小藥片 有的和你頭一樣大\N{\fs38}Oh, uh, round ones, small ones, ones as big as your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說我的惡夢了\N{\fs38}But enough about my nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么信啊\N{\fs38}What kind of mail do you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 兄弟 大房間很好吧\N{\fs38}Hey, buddy. Enjoying the big room? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的原話是"Graham想對他的房間怎么著\N{\fs38}Dad's exact words were "Graham can do whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怎么著" 大概是這樣啦\N{\fs38}he wants with the room"... or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 如果我能說服他把房間給我\N{\fs38}Ergo, if I get Graham to want to give me the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就歸我了\N{\fs38}hmm, it's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間發生過很多事啊 好的\N{\fs38}So much happened in this room... good things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 可怕的  - 可怕的\N{\fs38}- some scary things. - Scary things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 沒什么好說的\N{\fs38}Oh, hardly even worth talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是貓幽靈什么的\N{\fs38}Like Shadowpuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- "貓幽靈"  - 嗯 這是我的叫法\N{\fs38}- "Shadowpuss"? - Well, that's what I called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的真實名字是人類無法發出的音\N{\fs38}His real name can't be made by human vocal cords...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是很典型長著貓臉的地獄生物\N{\fs38}basically your average cat-faced hell creature
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 同時有著惡魔的身體  - 噢\N{\fs38}- with the body of a demon. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等上鉤了\N{\fs38}The hook was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 過去夜里經常出現一只老貓 就在那個門后面\N{\fs38}Yep, used to see the old puss at night, right behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說他會吃掉你的內臟 \N{\fs38}Legend has it he would eat your entrails and keep you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你眼睜睜看著他擺弄糟蹋你的玩具\N{\fs38}alive to watch while he played carelessly with your toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的床周圍有火山熔巖保護\N{\fs38}Well, my bed's surrounded by a lava force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓幽靈就是在火山巖里出生的\N{\fs38}Well, Shadowpuss was born in lava,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那阻止不了他 好自為之吧 再見\N{\fs38}so that's not really gonna be a problem for him. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 今天就這樣吧 一共是175美元 \N{\fs38}Oh, well, that's our time for today. That'll be $175.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是我的臺詞\N{\fs38}Hey, that's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Annie\N{\fs38}Hey, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還沒有自我介紹呢\N{\fs38}I don't think we were properly introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Bill\N{\fs38}the other night... I'm Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很高興見到你 Bill\N{\fs38}Well, it's very nice to meet you, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我是個精神科醫生\N{\fs38}By the way, I'm a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你對你的藥有任何疑問 我就在樓上 15B\N{\fs38}If you have any questions about your meds, upstairs in 15-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的藥  - 好了 Bill\N{\fs38}- My meds? - Come on, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有在計時了 公歸公私歸私\N{\fs38}You're off the clock. Leave work at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike跟我說的我會嚴格保密的\N{\fs38}What Mike told me was in strictest confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 只想告訴你 你可以來找我  - 呃 很好  \N{\fs38}- I just want you to know I'm a resource. - Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躁郁癥 得多上點心啊\N{\fs38}Bipolar disorder... is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躁郁癥\N{\fs38}Bipolar disorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是得聽聽別人的意見嘛\N{\fs38}We can get a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信 你居然告訴那家伙我有躁郁癥\N{\fs38}I can't believe you told that guy I was bipolar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么知道你沒有呢\N{\fs38}Well, do we know for a fact you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我只是不想鄰居討厭我們\N{\fs38}Look, I'd just prefer if our neighbors didn't hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想幫你收拾\N{\fs38}I mean, I was just trying to clean up your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"殘局" 我的殘局\N{\fs38}"Mess"? My mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就想這么說吧  - 我打算漸弱處理的\N{\fs38}- You were about to say "My mess." - I was gonna just trail off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候你待人太不友善了\N{\fs38}Sometimes you're a little hard on people,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不一次次去補救\N{\fs38}and I have to smooth things over from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次次 所以你以前也做過了\N{\fs38}Time to time? So you've done this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 在大樓里那次\N{\fs38}Well, in the building and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鐵上那次 還有兒童動物園那次\N{\fs38}on the subway and, uh, at the petting zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是不是五歲\N{\fs38}I don't care if you're five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能騎駱駝就是不能騎\N{\fs38}You're not supposed to ride the llama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會教訓舉止粗魯的人\N{\fs38}Yes! I call people out on their rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為這有什么問題\N{\fs38}I don't think there's anything wrong with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們可以把我看成文明社會\N{\fs38}You know, one could argue that I am all that stands
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和混亂之間的堅實守護者\N{\fs38}between civilized society and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是蝙蝠俠嗎  - 我是你妻子\N{\fs38}- You're Batman?! - I'm your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該統一戰線啊\N{\fs38}And we're supposed to be a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不意味著我要盲目贊同你\N{\fs38}That doesn't mean I'm gonna blindly agree
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我知道你是錯的\N{\fs38}with everything you say even if I think you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的嗎 所以你...  - 不要這樣拉長句子\N{\fs38}- Really? Is that why... - Don't stretch out words like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓我覺得很不安  - 不不不 沒事\N{\fs38}- because it's... that's unsettling. - No, no, no. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很高興知道\N{\fs38}It's just good for me to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不再互相支持了\N{\fs38}that we no longer have to get each other's backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好 很好\N{\fs38}Good, good, good, good, good, good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好 好極了\N{\fs38}Good, good, good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣更不安了\N{\fs38}That's even more unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我住的地方 那是煮飯的地方\N{\fs38}This is where I live. This is where I cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 酷  - 那是工作的地方\N{\fs38}- Cool. - This is where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好\N{\fs38}Hmm. Good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里 是你吻我的地方\N{\fs38}And this... is where you kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 Leigh姑姑  - 啊\N{\fs38}- Hello, Aunt Leigh. - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 你不能就這樣溜進別人的公寓\N{\fs38}Eve! You can't just sneak into somebody's apartment like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 相信我 我差點被槍殺了  - 嗨 你好嗎\N{\fs38}- Trust me. I've been shot at. - Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 小家伙在這呢\N{\fs38}Hey! Here's the little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit不在這兒真可惜\N{\fs38}Oh! I bet you wish Bandit was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 對嗎 對的  - 你剛才去哪了\N{\fs38}- Don't you? Yes, you do. - Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗跑出去了 我在樓下大廳找到的\N{\fs38}The dog got out. I found him in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓管不肯幫我修門\N{\fs38}The super won't fix my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他一直溜進來偷我的內衣\N{\fs38}I think he's sneaking in and stealing my underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近干的活一點錢都沒賺著\N{\fs38}I am working without a net right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這家伙是誰  - Gary\N{\fs38}- Who is this guy? - Gary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在狗狗公園遇到的\N{\fs38}I met at the dog park yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破冰者起作用了 成功破冰\N{\fs38}Icebreaker already worked... ice broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 能幫我照看一下小狗嗎\N{\fs38}Hey,do you mind watching Icebreaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Gary需要一點成人時間\N{\fs38}Gary and I were gonna have a little adult time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 破冰者保護欲太強了\N{\fs38}but, you know, Icebreaker is very protective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能會以為媽媽受傷了\N{\fs38}He might think Mommy's getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這借口沒"最近干活沒賺著錢"好\N{\fs38}I didn't think you could top "Working without a net."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 要不我去問下你爸  - 別 好吧 我來照看它\N{\fs38}- I guess I could just ask your Dad. - No! No. Uh... I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會最好給我精彩點\N{\fs38}This better be a good concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最棒了 幫我個忙\N{\fs38}You're the best. Listen, do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走的時候 跟這家伙自我介紹一下\N{\fs38}On your way out, introduce yourself to this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只有九成把握他叫Gary\N{\fs38}because I'm only 90% sure his name's Gary, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在Graham腦中埋下了貓幽靈的種子\N{\fs38}I had planted the seed of Shadowpuss in Graham's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要做的就是收獲恐懼的果實\N{\fs38}Now all I needed was to harvest my crop of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系緊安全帶咯\N{\fs38}Strap in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音文檔明顯載錯了\N{\fs38}That's obviously the wrong sound file.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么鬼東西啊 \N{\fs38}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 怎么啦 發生什么事啦 孩子們\N{\fs38}Hey, hey, what's going on? What's going on, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我做了這個來嚇貓幽靈  - 什么貓幽靈\N{\fs38}- I made him to scare Shadowpuss. - What's a Shadowpuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在我房間里一只恐怖的貓惡魔 Ian 快告訴他\N{\fs38}He's a scary demon cat that lives in my room. Ian, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真打算嚇你弟\N{\fs38}Are you seriously trying to scare your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓他跟你換房間嗎  - 我要睡大房 爸\N{\fs38}- into switching rooms with you? - I need a bigger room, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不把我當回事\N{\fs38}And you're not taking me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你手上拿著個貓木偶呢 - 這不是個木偶\N{\fs38}- You're holding a cat puppet. - This is not a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以展現38種不同的情緒\N{\fs38}It's capable of 38 distinct emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在真是有38種情緒了 Ian 自豪可不在里面\N{\fs38}I feel 38 emotions right now, Ian, and not one of them is pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉下它的尾巴 看有什么發生\N{\fs38}Pull its tail. See what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才不要拉\N{\fs38}No, I'm not gonna pull its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你想我們把你當成人對待\N{\fs38}Look, you want to be treated like an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別再糾結誰睡大房 計劃下將來\N{\fs38}stop worrying about who gets a bigger room and find a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我有計劃的  - 是嗎 你從大學輟學\N{\fs38}- Oh, I have a path. - Really? You dropped out of college.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這四個月了 還沒收你房租\N{\fs38}You've been here four months, rent-free. I mean, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ian 你很聰明 可是專注力放錯了地方\N{\fs38}a smart kid, Ian, but you're focusing on the wrong things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 還給我  - 不行\N{\fs38}- Give me this. - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Graham要有充足睡眠 他是我最后的希望了\N{\fs38}Graham's got to get some sleep... he's my last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊  - 發生了什么\N{\fs38}- Aah! - What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他拉了那尾巴  - 真是\N{\fs38}- He pulled its tail. - Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh姑姑的狗在這干嘛\N{\fs38}What's Aunt Leigh's dog doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz(16.9,200,100,1200)}{\pos(460,250)}{\fs38}{\shad0}{\fn微軟雅黑} 躁郁癥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它帶來給你看看\N{\fs38}I... brought him here to show you what a good
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh姑姑把它照顧得多好\N{\fs38}job Aunt Leigh's been doing of taking care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在和Gary在大西洋城\N{\fs38}She's in Atlantic City with Gary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人其實叫Steve\N{\fs38}whose name turned out to be Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會就在今晚 我想我贏了\N{\fs38}And since the concert is tonight, I guess I won the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Leigh姑姑呢  - 找獸醫去了\N{\fs38}- Where is Aunt Leigh? - She's... at the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不帶狗去嗎  - 你\N{\fs38}- Without the dog? - You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能把狗帶到獸醫診所啊\N{\fs38}You can't take a dog to a veterinary clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 空氣里到處是犬類病毒\N{\fs38}You know, all those... those airborne canine viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且 城里正開貓咪大會呢\N{\fs38}Plus, there's that cat convention in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 演唱會沒戲\N{\fs38}Got it. No concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為 Eve應該去看演唱會\N{\fs38}Actually... I think Eve should go to the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么  - 我一直都是同意的\N{\fs38}- What? - I never had a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve那么聰明 我相信她的判斷力\N{\fs38}Eve's smart. I trust her judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不用非得贏了賭局才能去\N{\fs38}She shouldn't have to win a bet to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等一下  - 太好了\N{\fs38}- Hang on. - Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們改變決定前我先走了\N{\fs38}I'm getting out of here before that answer can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不懂 我們決定好的啊  - 不不 那是你的決定\N{\fs38}- I don't understand. We decided. - No, no, no, no. You decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我們是同一戰線的才支持你的\N{\fs38}I backed you up because we're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在 我們之間不需再"盲目附和"\N{\fs38}But now, since we don't have to always
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以有自己意見\N{\fs38}"Blindly agree," I can give my own opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給Harris打個電話\N{\fs38}You know, I think I'm gonna give Harris a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不不 別打  - 就打\N{\fs38}- No. No, you wouldn't. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 聽著 把Eve推向了龍潭虎穴是一回事\N{\fs38}No, look, it's one thing to throw Eve into harm's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可卡拉OK 我倆就得一起進龍潭虎穴啦\N{\fs38}but karaoke... you'd be going down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像瓊斯鎮一樣\N{\fs38}It'll be like Jonestown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}人民圣殿教教徒集體自殺慘劇之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少這是他們都同意的啊\N{\fs38}At least they were a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Harris 我是Annie\N{\fs38}Harris, hi. It's Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你知道嗎 我的感冒突然痊愈了\N{\fs38}Hey, you know what? My fever just broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 今晚見\N{\fs38}Well, then we will see you tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 這是狗吃過的\N{\fs38}Okay, that's been in a dog's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- *我們兩心相依*  - *眼里只有你*\N{\fs38}- *That is what we are* - *No one in between*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- *眼里只有你*  - *未來會怎樣*\N{\fs38}- *no one in between * - *how can we be wrong?*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*伴我去遠航* *駛向太平洋*\N{\fs38}*sail away with me* *to another world*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 下一個就是你咯  - 是啊\N{\fs38}- You realize you're up next. - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊早藥效過去前把歌唱完\N{\fs38}I can get my song in before my meds wear off
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后像Claire Danes一樣在這兒撒瘋\N{\fs38}and I get all Claire Danes in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}<國土安全>女主扮演者 片中患有躁郁癥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那只是她演的角色而已\N{\fs38}You know, that's just a character she plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看過她上艾倫秀 真人挺好的\N{\fs38}I saw her on Ellen. She was... she was lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}美國一檔脫口秀節目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要上去嗎\N{\fs38}You're really gonna go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是說 你已經證實了你的觀點  - 謝謝大家\N{\fs38}- Well, you've proved your point. - Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 咱倆都知道你不喜歡卡拉OK  - 好啦\N{\fs38}- We both know you hate karaoke. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝Kay Costa扮演的多莉·帕頓\N{\fs38}Let's hear it for Kay Costa as Dolly Parton!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一位  \N{\fs38}All right, next up... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱烈歡迎首次在這舞臺演唱的 Annie Henry\N{\fs38}Ah, for the first time on this stage, we have Annie Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也沒有機會退縮咯\N{\fs38}Last chance to back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 Mike 我就是要上去\N{\fs38}Well, you know, Mike, I think I'm gonna just go up there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀出我最好的表演\N{\fs38}and give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NBC4臺 今夜一起跟著音樂搖滾起來吧\N{\fs38}NBC4, we are gonna rock this place tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躁郁癥嗎\N{\fs38}Bipolar disorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這也拿出來開玩笑 Claire Danes才是\N{\fs38}That's nothing to joke about, man. Claire Danes has that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她沒有 她只是個才華橫溢的演員而已\N{\fs38}No, she doesn't. She's just an incredibly gifted actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜猜 肯德基爺爺嗎\N{\fs38}Let me guess... Colonel Sanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯你個頭 Doug 說說看肯德基爺爺唱了什么歌\N{\fs38}Pull your head out, Doug. Name one song by Colonel Sanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 美味吮指歌嗎  - 那又不是他的歌\N{\fs38}- The finger-lickin' good song? - That's not a song.
