Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮的是肯尼·羅杰斯 哪涼快去哪吧 Doug\N{\fs38}I'm Kenny Rogers. Keep moving, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}美國鄉村音樂歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么你不跟Annie道歉\N{\fs38}I just don't get why you don't apologize to Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥 我還能怎么做\N{\fs38}For what? What was I supposed to do?
