Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以比起你老婆 你更關心你的好鄰居咯\N{\fs38}So you're more concerned about your neighbor than your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那個傳說中不喜歡卡拉OK的人\N{\fs38}And by the way, for somebody who supposedly hates karaoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很享受嘛\N{\fs38}she sure seems to be enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著她在臺上\N{\fs38}Seeing her up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才發現她并不是要跟我對著干\N{\fs38}I realized she wasn't trying to make a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的喜歡卡拉OK\N{\fs38}She actually loved karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這些年來她一直假裝不喜歡\N{\fs38}She'd just been pretending to hate it all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是為了和我統一戰線\N{\fs38}to be a team player.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 再次感謝Annie Henry  - 謝謝大家\N{\fs38}- That was Annie Henry... - Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她這首超長版<Hit Me With Your Best Shot>\N{\fs38}With a very extended version of Hit Me With Your Best Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位是\N{\fs38}And next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 瞧瞧\N{\fs38}Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Annie Henry\N{\fs38}It's Annie Henry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 又是她 - 還來啊\N{\fs38}- Again. - Two in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"一整晚"這句唱的可真恰當\N{\fs38}"All Night Long" Is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么時候能輪到我唱啊 - 我要站在Annie那邊\N{\fs38}- When will I get to sing? - I wanted to have Annie's back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟這么些年來她一直站在我這邊一樣\N{\fs38}the way she's had mine all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我了\N{\fs38}It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出現了一個絕好的機會\N{\fs38}And then an opportunity presented itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干嘛呢 Doug - 我只是\N{\fs38}- What the hell, Doug? - I-I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie是報過名的 你怎么能在她唱歌的時候搶話筒呢\N{\fs38}Annie signed up. You can't cut her off in the middle of a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是你的專場秀 Doug\N{\fs38}It's not all about Doug, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一回 我知道Annie為什么喜歡朝人大喊了\N{\fs38}For the first time, I got why Annie loves calling people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是一種沖動\N{\fs38}It's... it's kind of a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也有可能會有些過激\N{\fs38}although it's possible I might have gone a bit too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有 Doug 如果你不這么粗魯\N{\fs38}And another thing, Doug... if you weren't so rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能就不會是世界上最老的實習生了\N{\fs38}you might not be the world's oldest intern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦 不 - 還有你猜怎么著\N{\fs38}- Oh, no. - And guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒人想要看你的即興演出 - 該死 Mike\N{\fs38}- Nobody wants to see your improv show. - Aw, damn it, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我不得不看"注意:前方高能"了\N{\fs38}Now I got to go see Caution: May Contain Nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}油管上一檔神經病脫口秀節目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Doug準備幫我\N{\fs38}Um... Mike? Doug was gonna do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 伴唱Jambo Jambo那部分呢 - 我在單子上的\N{\fs38}- the "Jambo Jambo" Part for me. - I'm... I'm on the sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是么 這是你名字 Doug D-o-u-g\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, there you are. Doug, D-o-u-g.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 Jambo Jambo\N{\fs38}All right, Jambo Jambo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 算了 我不想跳了 - 報名了就要來 Doug Jambo\N{\fs38}- No, I'd really rather not. - Respect the sheet, Doug. Jambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛 Jambo\N{\fs38}Come on, Jambo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 快點 我們走\N{\fs38}Eve, come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 我們就要晚了\N{\fs38}Come on, we're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死\N{\fs38}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為啥我總避免喜歡上什么\N{\fs38}This is why I try not to like things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 哈嘍\N{\fs38}Hi. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你毀氣氛啊 Mike\N{\fs38}Thanks for killing the vibe, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 變裝整個啥用都沒有了 - 抱歉了\N{\fs38}- A whole costume change for nothing. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要支持你 你知道的 和你一樣\N{\fs38}I-I just wanted to have your back, you know, do what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是這么干的 我是對著他們的壞習慣大喊\N{\fs38}That's not what I do. I call people out on their bad behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然對一個無辜的45實習生開槍\N{\fs38}You took a shot at an innocent 45-year-old intern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他才32 - 哇哦\N{\fs38}- He's 32. - Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多喝點水啊\N{\fs38}Have a glass of water every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我可能\N{\fs38}Okay, I may have gone a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對電梯那個男的有點過分了\N{\fs38}little too far with the guy in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 罵了十層樓吧 - 盡管如此 經歷了今晚\N{\fs38}- Yeah, about ten floors. - Even so... I think after tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯還是我比較善于與人對質\N{\fs38}it's obvious that I am better at confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧 我倒是一點都不享受 - 真的 我挺喜歡的\N{\fs38}- Yeah, I didn't enjoy that at all. - Exactly. And I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個瘋狂的想法\N{\fs38}So here's a crazy idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不從今往后 咱就固守自己擅長的活兒\N{\fs38}how about from now on, we just stick to what we do best?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來對付混蛋\N{\fs38}I'll take on the jerks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來保證我們還會被邀請進派對\N{\fs38}and you make sure we still get invited to parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交 不過這個派對大概泡湯了\N{\fs38}Done. Although I think this one's off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會計部的Alice一直想用眼神殺死我\N{\fs38}Alice from accounting keeps giving me the death stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那個不用管 我來搞定她\N{\fs38}Oh, don't worry about it. I'll take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 你怎么沒去音樂會啊\N{\fs38}Eve. Why aren't you at the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了贏得賭注 我一直偷偷在養破冰者\N{\fs38}I've been secretly taking care of Icebreaker to win the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh姑姑的事 老爸說的對 我正要出門的時候\N{\fs38}Dad was right about Aunt Leigh. I was on my way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見狗狗在大廳里 于是就這樣了\N{\fs38}and I saw the dog in the lobby, so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 把狗繩子給我 - 什么\N{\fs38}- Give me the leash. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽是對的 你有自己的判斷\N{\fs38}Mom was right. You do have good judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 去吧 去音樂會吧 - 真的嗎 謝謝你 老爸\N{\fs38}- Now, go to the concert. - Seriously? Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這會是我的"涅槃"時刻\N{\fs38}Oh, this is going to be my Nirvana moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是"紅辣椒"時刻就成\N{\fs38}As long as it's not your Red Hot Chili Peppers moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}也是美國搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我搶到了他們四個人的襪子 - 那快走吧 都9點了\N{\fs38}- I got all four socks. - So hop on a train. It's 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還能趕上最后一首歌\N{\fs38}You should be there for the last song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的音樂會一般都會超過11點的\N{\fs38}Oh, they don't even go on until 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他們怎么著 - 趁著你們沒改主意\N{\fs38}- They don't what? - I'm getting out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先撤了\N{\fs38}before that answer can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 你買了治療狗啊\N{\fs38}Hey! You got a therapy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 Annie\N{\fs38}Good call, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾蛋吧 Bill\N{\fs38}Suck it, Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不罵白不罵\N{\fs38}I'm just gonna own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 老爸 - 嗨\N{\fs38}- Hey, Dad. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對 我一直把精力放在錯誤的事兒上\N{\fs38}You were right... I've been focusing on the wrong things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個月初 你會收到我的租金支票\N{\fs38}But first of the month, you're gonna get a rent check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一點康奈爾大學退還我的飯錢\N{\fs38}I got a little money back when Cornell refunded my meal plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那其實還是我的錢\N{\fs38}Yeah, that's actually my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 但是我還把貓幽靈放網上賣了500刀\N{\fs38}Right, but I also sold Shadowpuss on Craigslist for $500.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟買家說尾巴的事兒了嗎\N{\fs38}Did you tell them about the tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得買家不會需要這功能的\N{\fs38}I don't think they're going to be using it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 買家只問我能不能洗 - 老天\N{\fs38}- They asked if it's washable. - God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我準備找份工作\N{\fs38}And I'm going to get a job too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現我的夢想也許還有一段路要走\N{\fs38}It might take a little longer to reach my dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已經是成人了 你覺得租金多少比較合適\N{\fs38}but, hey, I'm a grown-up. What do you think is fair rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐約平均水平來說\N{\fs38}In New York City? Ballpark?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 1200刀 - 不是 我說的可是小房間\N{\fs38}- $1,200. - No, I'm talking about the tiny room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fs38}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人其實就像跟一個團隊一樣\N{\fs38}Being in a family is kind of like being on a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 小家伙 - 怎么了 你眼睛都紅了\N{\fs38}- Hey, little guy. - What's going on? Your eyes are all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛跟Gary分手\N{\fs38}I just broke up with Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他親他家狗的樣子 太深情了\N{\fs38}I saw the way he kissed his dog... very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒那么親過我\N{\fs38}He'll never kiss me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不一定能挑你隊友\N{\fs38}You don't always get to pick your teammates...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都哭了一整天了 關鍵是我根本不喜歡這男的\N{\fs38}I've been crying all day, and I didn't really even like this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你是對狗狗過敏吧\N{\fs38}I think you're allergic to the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 Michael 我對自己的狗狗\N{\fs38}Oh, please, Michael. Don't you think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不過敏 我還不知道么\N{\fs38}I'd know if I was allergic to my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你說的對\N{\fs38}No, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把破冰者送回去了\N{\fs38}Oh, but I can't take Icebreaker back to the pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也不會贏得每一場比賽\N{\fs38}...and you might not win every game...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我養狗嗎\N{\fs38}You want me to take the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才不是那種人\N{\fs38}No, I don't want to be that person that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不論發生什么 你們都要一起渡過\N{\fs38}But no matter what happens, you go through it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養一個吉祥物也沒什么\N{\fs38}And it doesn't hurt to have a mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 各位 我們家要有狗狗了\N{\fs38}Hey, everybody, we got a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓我看看 - 哦\N{\fs38}- Let me see! - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜這狗不用付租金吧\N{\fs38}I bet the dog doesn't have to pay rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 它跟你住\N{\fs38}That's 'cause he's sharing your room.
